data.title: Demand Webcasts from Solid Solutions
data.meta_description: Register today to view our free webcasts about multiple functions that can be used within SOLIDWORKS. We provide regular SOLIDWORKS webcasts on a weekly basis from Solid Solutions.
data.text:
TriMech’s Enterprise Solutions Team brings together experts from Adaptive, Forward Vision, Design Rule, Desktop Engineering, and Majenta Solutions Dassault Systèmes Division to form an elite solutions team.

The team's core function is to use their wealth of experience to deliver enterprise solutions from the Dassault Systèmes portfolio of products and solutions, including CATIA, DELMIA, ENOVIA, SIMULIA and the 3DEXPERIENCE Platform.

Explore the TriMech Enterpise site to find the full portfolio and more information on our offerings.

Solid People are a specialist CAD recruitment agency and part of the TriMech group.

With their extensive network and thorough knowledge of the CAD recruitment industry Solid People can match candidates to your needs quickly and accurately.

They manage the full process from sourcing to starting and regardless of your choice of CAD tools or what you're designing. So if you're looking to find a suitable CAD professional for your business then visit their site to learn more.
